{
  "stem": "3659.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So basically, I didn't go to school in this country, with the exception of that short period of time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And whatever I have learned, I have learned through life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't have the formal education, that you would say that if you achieve a lot in your life that this is through total formal education.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I believe in learning, very, very important.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it's actual hands on that will teach you what not to do rather than what to do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so we just kept going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And unfortunately, my dad had a heart attack when-- after about four years, and as a young man, and lost his business.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But that didn't stop us from not going forward.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I did a complete turnaround, and I became-- I went into the garment industry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I became-- sales in a-- in the showrooms, and I was very successful in that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I also did modeling in the showrooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was just about-- yes, you're right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was just going-- yeah, I was 20.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I worked there full time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for that-- for-- for a 20-year-old or 21-year-old, the salary I received was very good.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was $75 a week, which was incredible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I had the sales that I did there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I got quite an education in the garment industry, quite an education, which was good in many cases.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It-- it taught me of what not to do a lot of times of the things I saw and learned there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then I got-- I met a young man, and I got married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An American.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An American.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I became pregnant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I married in '48, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and my son was born in 1950.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
